reviews_data.review_text:
$7  for a cup of watered down ice coffee That's basically all milk. I said to add less milk and the girl couldn't get it right. Three times.
Very rude.I spoke nicely and gave instructions to the cashier. I wanted less milk because the last time It was Way too milky.
I will never come to this establishment again and surely spread the word.
Overall I like this place and haven’t had any problems yet.
Great for coffee and tea drinkers alike. Tiramisu latte is not to be missed !
Even days later I'm shocked I payed 8 dollars for a cup of murky bean water
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Joolee,

We're so sorry to hear your drink was not up to par. Please feel free to reach out to ballantyne@summitcoffee.com with more detail. We are also always happy to make your drink right during your stay at the shop. We hope you will try us out again soon. Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: I try to get out here a couple of times a month, always have a great latte!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Will,

Thank you for the 5 star review! We appreciate your commitment and love that you come to us for your latte fix. We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Very dirty
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Rosa,

We're sorry to hear your visit was worth a low review. Being a clean and calming atmosphere is what we strive for. We hope you give us another try soon. Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: The most friendly staff and service is on point. I love meeting here and they have great patio seating!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Dianna,

You're too kind! We really strive for the utmost form of hospitality here. We love our patio too! We hope to see you again soon and thank you for the sweet review

reviews_data.review_text: So happy that this place opened! A GREAT spot to get a GREAT cup of coffee! This is exactly what this area needed! Wishing all the success in the world to the new owners and proprietors of this fantastic coffee shop who are wonderful family-oriented people!
reviews_data.owner_answer: This is too kind!! Thank you so much for your support!

reviews_data.review_text: Very cute place that taught me something new about coffee?! I got the latte they advertised on their chalkboard and got it with heavy cream instead of milk?! Haha can't believe I never heard of that. It was soooo good.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Madeleine,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us a 5 star review! We're so glad we could introduce you to something new and that you had a great experience. Please come again soon! Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: We were in Charlotte and went there for two days and just got coffee, but the coffee was hot and delicious and the service was great. The first time we drink some there and then left with it and then the second time we took it to go. It’s very small and little place but they were pretty quick and very helpful.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Sue,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us this 5 star review! We hope we can be your go-to again when you're back in the Charlotte area. Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: Yummy chais & matcha! Super friendly staff who really care about whether you are happy with your drink! Add some of their house syrups for great added flavor. This location is much smaller than other Summits in Clt, so it’s limited indoor seating but there’s outdoor seating if it’s nice outside.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hannah,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us a 5 star review! It's really important to us that we make sure our guests have an amazing experience from when they come in to when they leave. We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Very rude staff but Coffee was at least better than Starbucks!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
TJ,

We're so sorry to hear you did not have the best experience with us. Please reach out to ballantyne@summitcoffee.com so we can hear more. Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text:
WOW!!! I walked in after not visiting for a year because of life and… too much caffeine for me! Ha!!…. But wait… Marisa recognized me and remembered me!!!
She is sweet, patient and kind!! She is a gem 💎 and I’m grateful to know that people still care like Marisa at Summit Coffee in Ballantyne!! (Charlotte, NC). The coffee is tasty and strong!!! The carrot cake and blueberry muffin…OH so gooood!!! The service and atmosphere are fun, fresh and inviting….. I came to warm up in the cold and left with a smile!! 😃
Marisa made the difference!! People matter and kindness goes a loooooong way!!!
Thank you Marisa!!!! I appreciate you!!! I’ll be back!!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Sarah,

Thank you for taking the time to leave this thoughtful 5 star review! We will pass this review along to her. We hope to see you again soon, thank you!

reviews_data.review_text:
EDIT: These guys responded and said they only put 2 shots in a 24 oz. That’s actually heinous 😭 Dropping to 1 star

Been to this location twice over the last few weeks and have been disappointed on the quality. First time, I got the seasonal sugar cookie latte and then a caramel latte, both their larger size (24 oz) and iced.

Both drinks have tasted more like a milk than a latte. I’m not sure if there is supposed to be another shot of espresso in it, but it feels very lacking in the coffee taste.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Aidan,

We're so sorry the quality of your drink was not what you expected it to be. All sizes of our drinks come with two shots each. So often times if you prefer a stronger tasting coffee, you can add in an extra shot or size down to achieve what you're looking for. Also, always feel free to let us know if you're drink isn't what you'd like it to be and we will happily make adjustments for you. We hope you'll give us another chance soon! Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text:
Cool quaint little spot!
They have delicious drinks every time we visit. Their food is an area that probably could be amped up a bit but overall, great spot to get a drink and chat.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Brad,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us a 5 star review! We're always taking customer input on how our food selection can improve. If you have any suggestions, please feel free to reach out to ballantyne@summitcoffee.com we would love to hear from you. We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: The 3 star review is mainly for the outrageous price I paid for a large vanilla latte with oat milk, 9$!! Plus of course they ask for tip as well so 10$ for a cup of coffee all in all. Sorry that's just morally wrong and on principle I won't be returning to get completely ripped off. Yes I ordered a large and upgraded with oatmilk but no, it should still not cost that.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi,

Thank you for taking the time to share your experience with us. We understand that finding reasonable prices is an important factor in our customers experience. With being a specialty coffee shop, we continually work to offer competitive pricing while providing top-notch products for our customers. We appreciate your feedback and will be taking this into consideration. Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: Hip.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Duncan,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us a 5 star review! We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Better than Starbucks! & The staff there is amazing
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Ernie,

Thank you for the 5 star review! We take so much pride in our quality over here and we're glad that we could check those boxes for you. Please come back and visit soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Love this gem of a coffee shop! Sweet and attentive staff as well as delicious flavors throughout the year!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Sita,

Thank you for taking the time to leave a 5 star review! We appreciate you always being a loyal customer at our cafe. We will see you soon!

reviews_data.review_text: My latte was iced milk, and the scone was a brick. Very disappointed in the food, but service was lovely. My companion said her coffee was okay.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Kymberlee,

We're so sorry the food and drink wasn't what you expected it to be. We are always happy to re-make any drink for yourself or any customer if that is the case. Our baristas are always great at giving recommendations based off your preferences. We hope you'll give us another try in the near future.

reviews_data.review_text: I came in to get a gift card for a colleague and decided to give it a try. Compared to Starbucks, I enjoyed Summit Coffee so much more. I had a vanilla mocha and coffee cake. The coffee was excellently brewed, a great taste without all the sugar and syrups that SB adds to their coffee. Their menu options are pretty good, including different coffees, pastries, and other drink options. It is fairly small on the inside of the shop,  but their patio area is nice and gives more room. This will be my new coffee spot!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hello!

Thank you for taking the time to leave this 5 star review! We take so much pride in our quality over here and we're glad that we could check those boxes for you. Please come back and visit soon!

reviews_data.review_text:
I was only here one time because I was escaping Hurricane Milton, but it was nice. I had my dog, and there were several outdoor eating spots. I ordered a vanilla latte and my husband got 4 shots of espresso. Both were exactly what we wanted.

For those who live in the area, they have a runners club.

Interesting side note, they serve a limited selection of beer and wine. They also have some merch if you wanted a T-shirt or beanie or bags of coffee.

I thought it was a cute idea to have anyone who wanted design a cup. It may be fun especially with children. There was a sign that said, “ask about children’s beverages”.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Jessica,

Thank you for the detailed and very thoughtful review! We're glad you stopped by and we hope you visit us again if you're ever in the area!

reviews_data.review_text: I love this coffee spot! The drinks are high quality and priced reasonably, my go to weekend spot!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Marcella,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us this review! We're so glad we are your go-to! We hope to see you again soon

reviews_data.review_text: The ambience is top tier. The iced matcha latte was nothing to write home about. Very relaxing, productive environment.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Trevor,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us a 5 star review! We hope you visit us again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Beautiful small coffee shop with tasty loose leaf tea and nice coffee selection. They offer a variety of delicious pastries as well.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Roman,

We're so glad you had a great experience at our shop. Thank you for the pictures as well! We hope to see you again soon.

reviews_data.review_text: I’ve been here before a couple times and I love their blueberry matcha but customer service today was a bit hostile and unfortunately, the matcha tasted like oat milk. (Had a lovely customer service experience when I was here this Monday though!)
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Mahader,

We are so sorry you had a poor experience at our shop. We don't take this lightly! We are always happy to re-make any drink for yourself or any customer if you were unhappy with what you had received. If you would so kindly reach out to us via email ballantyne@summitcoffee.com we would like to get to the bottom of your experience with us. Our first priority is to make sure our customers are respected and satisfied. Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: It’s a good experience overall with the place and the staff, coffee and food is not good.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Sandeep,

Thank you for taking the time to share your feedback with us. Please email ballantyne@summitcoffee with your experience in more detail so we can get to the bottom of this!

reviews_data.review_text: The drip coffee here is great!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Sri,

Thank you for visiting us! We hope to see you again soon.

reviews_data.review_text: BEST coffee in Ballantyne. Service is great and they offer more than coffee with networking events and music. You should definitely check them out!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Christina,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us a review. We're so glad you had a great experience. We hope to see you again, soon!

reviews_data.review_text:
I'm thrilled to share my latest discovery with fellow coffee enthusiasts - a cozy gem that has stolen my heart and satisfied my caffeine cravings. This charming coffee shop is a must-visit for anyone seeking a delightful atmosphere and exceptional coffee.
The summer menu was very well thought out.  We tried the DreamSicle and the SummerCamp and they did not disappoint. I highly recommend stopping by Summit when you are in the Ballantyne area.  Enjoy your day!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Samantha,

Thank you for your thoughtful review and taking the time to come visit us. We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Such a cute little spot! All of our coffees were excellent and the big bun just topped it off! It was my first time ever trying Summit Coffee, as I was visiting from out of town, but it was so delicious! I ended up finding other locations to visit because of it! I’ll be back next time I’m in town!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Felicia,

Thank you for taking the time to check us out! We're so glad we could introduce you to the brand. We hope to see you again soon.

reviews_data.review_text:
Wish there was a 4.5.
5 stars means perfect. This place is awesome. Coffee roasted within dates well acceptable for each kind of roast. Very good not over sweetened or at all sour specialty drinks. There was live music and very kid friendly environment with kids playing with chalk outside.
Only a couple things could improve.
The water available didn't taste great.
Matcha was a little weak in flavor
And I wish the coffee had the type of wash added to the bags. Other than that. This is a phenomenal place. Highly recommend.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Culin,

Thank you for taking the time to share your feedback with us. Your experience is important and valuable to us. We will certainly take these matters into consideration as we continue to evolve as a business. We hope to see you again soon and, we would be happy to answer any retail coffee questions you may have going forward!

reviews_data.review_text: Yummy lattes and friendly service!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Jenna,

We're so glad you had an amazing experience with us. We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Great tasting coffee and baked goods. They even have vegan options for both coffee and baked goods and it all tastes great.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Gangadhar,

Thank you for sharing your feedback on our vegan options. The coffee cake is one of our favorites. We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Great little coffee shop in the Ballantyne area! We stopped here before work because the Starbucks line is insane over here. Their prices were very reasonable, and the coffee was delicious! The two females working were very nice as well. There is plenty of room for parking, too.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Steven,

Thank you for sharing your experience here with us. We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Coffee was fine but $.75 for oat or almond milk?  Retail the cost difference is pennies.  Why?  $5.50 for a coffee and you want to add $.75….
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Brad,

Thank you for visiting and taking the time to share your feedback. We understand your concern regarding the additional cost tied to oat and almond milk. Your feedback is important and valuable to us, and we will certainly take it into consideration as we continue to evolve our service. Thank you again. We hope to see you soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Cool little shop serving a variety of drinks. I got a Berries & Cream and Babe had the Berry Fresh. Both were delightfully refreshing. Indoor and outdoor seating available.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Deanna,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us this review. We are so glad you had a great experience.

reviews_data.review_text: Very good coffee,good prices, great staff! Our Saturday morning go-to spot. Try the BigBun!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Dana,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us this 5 star review! We're so glad you had a great experience and we can be apart of your weekly routine!

reviews_data.review_text:
I love going to Summit in the mornings before work and the team that works there is SO KIND and always very friendly. It’s definitely a highlight of my week.

Also, it should be said that the coffee is delicious. I order the same thing every time: a latte with oat milk and I love it each time.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Micah,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us this 5 star review. We appreciate your kind words!

reviews_data.review_text: This coffee shop is cozy! The staff there are super nice and will answer any questions you may have! The coffee is around the same price of the Starbucks close to it, but the quality of Summit quickly establishes that is worth going to over the former. The shop itself is a little small with limited seating, but that doesn't affect the service and atmosphere.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Kassidy,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us this 5 start review! We really focus in on the quality of our items and making sure we hold a welcoming and safe atmosphere!

reviews_data.review_text: Coffee good, service nice,although cappuccino is too tiny
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Venus,

We only offer our cappuccinos in a 6oz size. A latte may be something similar to try next visit where we offer various larger sizes. Thank you for taking the time to leave us this review!

reviews_data.review_text: The cookies and cream latte my wife ordered was simply delightful – a perfect blend of rich coffee and creamy sweetness. Highly recommended for a delicious treat!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Abhi,

The cookies and cream latte was a customer favorite! We're glad you enjoyed it as much as we did!

reviews_data.review_text: Very kind staff produced a really great pair of lattes for my love and I. I support small business and I respect baristas —they were very nice.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Madoka,

Thank you for such a great review. We're pleased to hear you had a great experience!

reviews_data.review_text: Best coffee in the area! So glad a Summit opened in Ballantyne, because there are so few local coffee shops around unless you want to drive 20+ minutes to Southend. The staff are so sweet every single time I go in, and the seasonal coffee menus are absolutely amazing! I crave their Everything Danish literally all the time too
reviews_data.owner_answer:
L W,

Thank you for taking the time to leave us a great review! We hope to see you back in the cafe soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Feels like a coffee shop you'd see in a romance movie where the two main characters meet for the first time. Food is delicious and creative!
reviews_data.owner_answer: This is a great analogy! We're so glad you had a phenomenal experience with us, thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: Love to have another local coffee shop in the area. Super sweet staff and great cafe food. The everything cream cheese danish is a must!! I also love how they have an order ahead option with their app!
reviews_data.owner_answer: The everything cream cheese danish is one of our favorites too! Thank you for your kindness!

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee...
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the 5 star review! Hope you visit us again!

reviews_data.review_text:
Starbucks who??? When I first heard this location was going in right near a Starbucks I was shocked… but now I’m not! After experiencing the coffee, employees, and atmosphere why would anyone choose Starbucks!? The quality is incredible and the store is super cute and cozy.
Sure, there’s not the convenience of a drive thru but the baristas here are very quick and efficient so you won’t be waiting long for your first sip! Everything tastes fantastic! HIGHLY recommend!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for taking the time to leave us such a thoughtful review! We appreciate you and hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Not a lot of decent coffee options in the immediate area, so I’m happy to report that Summit coffee is very good.
reviews_data.owner_answer: That is great to hear, thank you! We hope you will visit us again

reviews_data.review_text: Noice!!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the 5 star review! Hope you visit us again!

reviews_data.review_text: Friendly staff, many items on the menu. Delicious coffee, but matcha tea is best whipped with an electric frother. There were particles in it. We forgot our glasses inside, came back in the evening and the girl returned them to us. I recommend!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for taking the time to leave us this review!

reviews_data.review_text: Easily the best coffee in the Ballantyne/Blakeney/waverly area. Nothing can top this place.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for checking us out. We hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Everyone is so friendly here. The coffee is great. This area has needed something like this for a long time!
reviews_data.owner_answer: We totally agree! Thank you for taking the time to leave us a great review!

reviews_data.review_text: Great taste and service
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for your kind words! We appreciate you taking the time to leave us a review!

reviews_data.review_text: Really enjoyed our visit on opening weekend. Despite the crowds, barista Dora made a super tasty maple sea salt chai. The space is super cute with warm wood tones and soothing tunes. Can't wait to visit again!
reviews_data.owner_answer: The maple sea salt chai was one of our favorites as well. Thank you for the thoughtful review!

reviews_data.review_text: Opening weekend in Ballantyne!
reviews_data.owner_answer: We're so glad you found us! Thank you for taking the time to write us!

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee and friendly staff!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for the lovely review!

reviews_data.review_text: Cool new spot in Ballantyne for a good coffee... atmosphere is great.  Glad to see a trendy place added to the Neighborhood...
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for stopping by, Joe! Glad you enjoyed your experience with us!
